---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
const mainHtml = '<main class="container-x py-12 sm:py-16">  <!-- Cabecera solo impresión --><div class="print-only hidden mb-4"> <h1 class="font-display text-2xl">Sergio Jurado</h1> <p class="text-sm text-ink-soft">Desenvolupador Fullstack · Disseny Creatiu Digital</p> <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-ink-muted"> [tu-email] · [tu-teléfono] · Terrassa, Catalunya · [tu-web] </p> <div class="rule mt-3"></div> </div> <!-- Hero --> <section class="reveal mb-12 sm:mb-16"> <p class="eyebrow">Fullstack i Creatiu Digital</p> <h1 class="mt-3 text-hero text-[clamp(2.25rem,7vw,4.5rem)] leading-[1.02]">Desenvolupador Fullstack · Disseny Creatiu Digital</h1> <p class="mt-5 max-w-prose text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-soft sm:text-lg">Construeixo productes web ràpids i bonics, del concepte al desplegament, cuidant el detall visual.</p> <div class="no-print mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm text-ink-muted"> <span>Terrassa, Catalunya</span> <a href="mailto:[tu-email]" class="link-underline">[tu-email]</a> <span>[tu-teléfono]</span> </div> </section> <div class="cv-grid grid gap-10 sm:gap-14 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.9fr]"> <!-- Columna izquierda --> <div class="space-y-10"> <section class="avoid-break"> <h2 class="eyebrow mb-4">Sobre mi</h2> <p class="text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">Desenvolupador fullstack amb sensibilitat de disseny. Treballo amb JavaScript/TypeScript al frontend i backend, i gaudeixo convertint idees en interfícies netes i experiències cuidades. Em moc entre el codi, la tipografia i el motion.</p> </section> <section class="avoid-break"> <h2 class="eyebrow mb-4">Habilitats</h2> <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"> <li class="chip">JavaScript / TypeScript</li><li class="chip">React · Astro · Next.js</li><li class="chip">Node.js · Express</li><li class="chip">Tailwind CSS · CSS modern</li><li class="chip">PostgreSQL · MongoDB</li><li class="chip">Figma · UI/UX</li><li class="chip">Motion / animació web</li><li class="chip">Git · CI/CD · Vercel</li> </ul> </section> <section class="avoid-break"> <h2 class="eyebrow mb-4">Formació</h2> <ul class="space-y-4"> <li> <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-medium text-ink">Grau en Enginyeria Informàtica</p> <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">Universitat · 2016 — 2020</p> </li><li> <p class="text-[0.95rem] font-medium text-ink">Especialització en UI/UX Design</p> <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted">Domestika / Coursera · 2021</p> </li> </ul> </section> </div> <!-- Columna derecha --> <div class="space-y-12"> <section> <h2 class="eyebrow mb-6">Experiència</h2> <div class="space-y-8"> <article class="avoid-break border-l-2 border-line pl-5"> <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-4"> <h3 class="font-display text-xl">Desenvolupador Fullstack</h3> <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted">2022 — Actualitat</span> </div> <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm font-medium text-accent">Estudi Pixel &amp; Code</p> <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5"> <li class="flex gap-2.5 text-[0.92rem] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft"> <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-none rounded-full bg-accent-soft"></span> <span>Desenvolupament d’aplicacions web amb React, Astro i Node des del disseny al desplegament.</span> </li><li class="flex gap-2.5 text-[0.92rem] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft"> <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-none rounded-full bg-accent-soft"></span> <span>Millora del rendiment (LCP &lt; 1,5s) i accessibilitat en projectes client.</span> </li><li class="flex gap-2.5 text-[0.92rem] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft"> <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-none rounded-full bg-accent-soft"></span> <span>Disseny de sistemes de components reutilitzables i guies d’estil.</span> </li> </ul> </article><article class="avoid-break border-l-2 border-line pl-5"> <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-4"> <h3 class="font-display text-xl">Frontend i Dissenyador Digital</h3> <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted">2020 — 2022</span> </div> <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm font-medium text-accent">Freelance</p> <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5"> <li class="flex gap-2.5 text-[0.92rem] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft"> <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-none rounded-full bg-accent-soft"></span> <span>Landing pages, portfolios i botigues per a petites marques.</span> </li><li class="flex gap-2.5 text-[0.92rem] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft"> <span class="mt-2 h-1 w-1 flex-none rounded-full bg-accent-soft"></span> <span>Identitat visual, tipografia i animacions de scroll.</span> </li> </ul> </article> </div> </section> <section> <h2 class="eyebrow mb-6">Projectes destacats</h2> <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2"> <a href="https://github.com/senseikatana/sga-vilaseca" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card avoid-break group block rounded-xl border border-line bg-paper-card p-5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-accent/40 hover:shadow-sm"> <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">React · TS · Hono · Bun</span> <h3 class="mt-2 font-display text-lg leading-snug">Novatecnica SGA</h3> <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">WMS fullstack amb React, TypeScript, Hono i Bun. Control d’inventari en temps real, picking per onades, escaneig de codis i panell amb mètriques.</p> <span class="no-print mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.78rem] font-medium text-ink-soft transition-colors group-hover:text-accent"> <svg class="h-[13px] w-[13px]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"> <path d="M12 .5C5.7.5.5 5.7.5 12c0 5.1 3.3 9.4 7.9 10.9.6.1.8-.2.8-.5v-1.7c-3.2.7-3.9-1.5-3.9-1.5-.5-1.3-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.1-.7.1-.7.1-.7 1.2.1 1.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 1 1.8 2.7 1.3 3.4 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.7-1.6-2.6-.3-5.3-1.3-5.3-5.7 0-1.3.5-2.3 1.2-3.1-.1-.3-.5-1.5.1-3.1 0 0 1-.3 3.3 1.2a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0C17 4.6 18 4.9 18 4.9c.6 1.6.2 2.8.1 3.1.8.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 3.1 0 4.4-2.7 5.4-5.3 5.7.4.4.8 1.1.8 2.2v3.3c0 .3.2.6.8.5A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 23.5 12C23.5 5.7 18.3.5 12 .5z"></path> </svg> Veure a GitHub </span> </a><a href="https://github.com/senseikatana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card avoid-break group block rounded-xl border border-line bg-paper-card p-5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-accent/40 hover:shadow-sm"> <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">Astro · E-commerce</span> <h3 class="mt-2 font-display text-lg leading-snug">Treslunas Boutique</h3> <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">Botiga online construïda amb Astro i base de dades integrada. Catàleg, disseny cuidat i enfocament en rendiment.</p> <span class="no-print mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.78rem] font-medium text-ink-soft transition-colors group-hover:text-accent"> <svg class="h-[13px] w-[13px]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"> <path d="M12 .5C5.7.5.5 5.7.5 12c0 5.1 3.3 9.4 7.9 10.9.6.1.8-.2.8-.5v-1.7c-3.2.7-3.9-1.5-3.9-1.5-.5-1.3-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.1-.7.1-.7.1-.7 1.2.1 1.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 1 1.8 2.7 1.3 3.4 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.7-1.6-2.6-.3-5.3-1.3-5.3-5.7 0-1.3.5-2.3 1.2-3.1-.1-.3-.5-1.5.1-3.1 0 0 1-.3 3.3 1.2a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0C17 4.6 18 4.9 18 4.9c.6 1.6.2 2.8.1 3.1.8.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 3.1 0 4.4-2.7 5.4-5.3 5.7.4.4.8 1.1.8 2.2v3.3c0 .3.2.6.8.5A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 23.5 12C23.5 5.7 18.3.5 12 .5z"></path> </svg> Veure a GitHub </span> </a><a href="https://github.com/senseikatana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card avoid-break group block rounded-xl border border-line bg-paper-card p-5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-accent/40 hover:shadow-sm"> <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">UI · HTML/CSS</span> <h3 class="mt-2 font-display text-lg leading-snug">Digital Bank App</h3> <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">Interfície d’aplicació bancària digital amb HTML i CSS, centrada en una UI neta i una experiència clara.</p> <span class="no-print mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.78rem] font-medium text-ink-soft transition-colors group-hover:text-accent"> <svg class="h-[13px] w-[13px]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"> <path d="M12 .5C5.7.5.5 5.7.5 12c0 5.1 3.3 9.4 7.9 10.9.6.1.8-.2.8-.5v-1.7c-3.2.7-3.9-1.5-3.9-1.5-.5-1.3-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.1-.7.1-.7.1-.7 1.2.1 1.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 1 1.8 2.7 1.3 3.4 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.7-1.6-2.6-.3-5.3-1.3-5.3-5.7 0-1.3.5-2.3 1.2-3.1-.1-.3-.5-1.5.1-3.1 0 0 1-.3 3.3 1.2a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0C17 4.6 18 4.9 18 4.9c.6 1.6.2 2.8.1 3.1.8.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 3.1 0 4.4-2.7 5.4-5.3 5.7.4.4.8 1.1.8 2.2v3.3c0 .3.2.6.8.5A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 23.5 12C23.5 5.7 18.3.5 12 .5z"></path> </svg> Veure a GitHub </span> </a><a href="https://github.com/senseikatana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card avoid-break group block rounded-xl border border-line bg-paper-card p-5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-accent/40 hover:shadow-sm"> <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-wider text-accent">TypeScript · Vite</span> <h3 class="mt-2 font-display text-lg leading-snug">Coffeeshop</h3> <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">App web de cafeteria amb TypeScript i Vite. Interfície moderna i components reutilitzables.</p> <span class="no-print mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[0.78rem] font-medium text-ink-soft transition-colors group-hover:text-accent"> <svg class="h-[13px] w-[13px]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"> <path d="M12 .5C5.7.5.5 5.7.5 12c0 5.1 3.3 9.4 7.9 10.9.6.1.8-.2.8-.5v-1.7c-3.2.7-3.9-1.5-3.9-1.5-.5-1.3-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.1-.7.1-.7.1-.7 1.2.1 1.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 1 1.8 2.7 1.3 3.4 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.7-1.6-2.6-.3-5.3-1.3-5.3-5.7 0-1.3.5-2.3 1.2-3.1-.1-.3-.5-1.5.1-3.1 0 0 1-.3 3.3 1.2a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0C17 4.6 18 4.9 18 4.9c.6 1.6.2 2.8.1 3.1.8.8 1.2 1.8 1.2 3.1 0 4.4-2.7 5.4-5.3 5.7.4.4.8 1.1.8 2.2v3.3c0 .3.2.6.8.5A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 23.5 12C23.5 5.7 18.3.5 12 .5z"></path> </svg> Veure a GitHub </span> </a> </div> </section> </div> </div>  </main>';
